Encapsulation is a technique use to binding data and method that operate on that data
into a single unit(class) while restricting direct access of the data from outside the
class.

Benefits:
1.Data Hiding -> Protect to accessing sensitive data.
2.Controlled Access => Only safe modification are allowed through setters.
3.Flexibility => You can change the internal implementation later without affectin outside code.
4.Better maintainability =>

How can it achieve.
1.Make variables private.
2.Provide public getter and setter method to access or update those variables.
